    <h3 class="mt3" id="overview">Summary</h3>
    <p>I co-founded, operated, and closed a design agency in the music industry from the end of 2014 to the end of 2016. Mocktail completed about 50 client engagements and was comprised of five talented artists and designers during its lifetime.</p>
    <p>Starting Mocktail allowed me to live abroad, tackle problems creatively, and learn the basics of practical entrepreneurship. I explored leadership, negotiation, risk tolerance, the practice of graphic design, my own art and taste, accounting, capitalism, and community-building.</p>
    <p>But most importantly, I made many friends.</p>
